  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow">Travel at your own speed and opt for a self-drive skiing or snowboarding holiday. Make the mountains your own by sightseeing from airport to accommodation - stop and take in the views, pause in local towns and villages for a bite to eat, spot the wildlife as you meander along.
<p><img src="/media/13081152/ice-driving.jpg" alt="Swiss Short Breaks" rel="858,410" /></p>
<span style="font-size: 24px; color: #023761;">Why travel by car</span><span style="font-size: 24px; font-style: italic; color: #023761;"></span><span style="font-size: 24px; color: #023761;">?</span><span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; color: #023761;"><br /><br /></span> <strong>Pack as much as you like</strong> – no need to worry about ski carriage or packing that extra ski jacket
<p><strong>You decide the pace</strong> – set off a day earlier and enjoy the journey at your own speed</p>
<p><strong>Freedom and flexibility</strong> – get off the beaten track and make some stops along the way</p>
<p><strong>Comfort and privacy</strong> – enjoy the journey with your close friends and family</p>
<p><strong>Extra ski day</strong> – arrive in time to drop your bags at your accommodation and go skiing on your first day- you could even do the same on your final day!</p>
<h3><strong>We can offer a self-drive option to any country or resort in Europe</strong></h3>
<p>Majority of our guests will choose to drive to <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a> due to it's close proximity to England. However for example, if you are living in <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a> and want to head to <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a> for your winter holiday, we can make that happen.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
