<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><span style="color: #023761; font-size: 24px;">Self-drive Ski Holiday FAQs</span><span style="color: #023761; font-size: 24px;"></span></h3>
<p><strong>How do I book? - </strong>To book self-drive, you must call to book on 01483 79 11 11.</p>
<p><strong>How much can I save? - </strong>It depends on which date you travel and the type and time of your channel crossing.</p>
<p><strong>Is the ferry crossing included in the price of my holiday? - </strong>Yes, the ferry crossing from Dover to Calais is included and we can arrange a Le Shuttle (formerly known as Eurotunnel) crossing as well.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; background: 0px 0px #ffffff; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;">Travel with confidence </h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; background: 0px 0px #ffffff; border: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; background: 0px 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 400;">When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; background: 0px 0px #ffffff; border: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><img src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png" alt="safehands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
